customHTML.value: Sign On

nodeDescription.value: Prompt the user to enter their username.
Send the user ID to SecurID and get the user's list of authentication methods.
Branch the flow based on the selected authentication method.
Tell the user to check their authentication device (such as a mobile phone) to complete the authentication process.

customHTML.value:
Check Your Device

Complete authentication on your mobile device.

nodeDescription.value: Poll SecurID until the authentication process is completed on the other device.
Show a failure message, and direct the user back to the beginning.
Branch the flow based on the result of the authentication process.
Continue polling SecurID until the authentication process is completed on the other device.
Prompt the user to select an authentication method. For tokens, prompt the user to authenticate with their token.
